des: WBR is an internet platform where people of all colors can enjoy a variety of programs that have inspiring music, provides a safe space for humans to learn about Black Culture and interests, and be an example to corporate structures of how to implement Equity and Empowerment into its daily operations comfortably making it an educational and spiritual experience for us all.
